mustache

The documentation of the mustache package.

mustache

(mustache:template str values)

takes the template string and a hashmap of values to interpolate. The documentation of the mustache format can be found here.

Parameters:

str: the template string

values: a hashmap of substitute keys and values(keys and values must be strings)

Complexity: O(n)

Returns: the templated string
